This one has been a long time coming! Our first interval treadmill run video has been a favorite for years and a second one has been highly requested. Get ready to sweat buckets, burn calories, and boost your metabolism in the most condensed time period possible! We'll be running at three different paces--base (jog), push (run), and all out (sprint), with no walking recoveries. Let's go!

This workout is inspired by Orange Theory treadmill workouts. Visit OrangeTheory.com to find a studio near you! *Not sponsored

There are three things we all do every day, and we could all be doing them better: Eat Move Rest! 🥗🏃‍♀️💤 Eat more plants, move your body daily, and get adequate rest--it's as simple as that!

Dusty & Erin Stanczyk combined their formal education in Communication Studies and Biology, coupled with their passion for health & wellness, to create their health & lifestyle coaching business, EatMoveRest. The couple specializes in what they like to call "Lifestyle Design." Through one-and-one and group coaching, workshops, retreats, and their social media presence, Dusty and Erin's mission is to help others realize their fullest potential and become the best version of themselves!

Be sure to Subscribe, share with friends, and visit EatMoveRest.com for more!
